window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Uncover the true magic that is in psilocybin mushrooms!</b></p> <p>There is renewed interest in the use of natural treatments for many of modern-day health problems. One of these treatments is the psilocybin mushroom, which is touted as the magic remedy for mental health problems, thanks to the psychoactive properties in these magic mushrooms.</p> <p><i>But how exactly do these mushrooms bring about the benefits; what is the science behind it?</i></p> <p><i>Aren’t some mushrooms poisonous; how do you stay safe as you use the mushrooms for their benefits?</i></p> <p><i>Is it possible to grow your own, and if so, how can you do it?</i></p> <p>This audiobook will answer these and any other questions you may have about psilocybin by taking a deep and wide coverage of the topic to give you more than enough knowledge of how to use magic mushrooms safely for various purposes!</p> <p><b>Here is a summary of what you will learn:</b></p> <p></p> <ul> <li>The basics about magic mushrooms, including what they are, the different varieties and species, how to use them, the effects, how they affect the brain, and more</li> <li>How to take the right dosages</li> <li>The possible dangers that come with use of magic mushrooms and how to stay safe</li> <li>How to get started with growing psilocybin mushrooms, including what you need, the different stages of growth, caring for the mushrooms, providing ideal conditions, dealing with problems that may arise, and more</li> <li>How to use psilocybin mushrooms for fighting various diseases</li> <li>How to store the mushrooms properly without damaging their potency</li> <li>Supporting studies about the effectiveness of psilocybin mushrooms for different purposes</li> <li>How to make magic mushroom spore syringes</li> <li>How to make sterilized agar plates and Petri dishes</li> <li>How to use the spore slurry method effectively</li> <li>The ins and outs of psilocybin mushroom incubation, cloning, and harvesting</li> <li>The ins and outs of Pf-tek for growing mushroom spores</li> <li>And much more!</li> </ul> <p>The audiobook breaks down the seemingly complex concepts of psilocybin use and growing using beginner-friendly language to enable you to start applying what you learn immediately!</p>"; 
